				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					Earthenware- that error is related to too many local sockets being opened up in the same port range.  If this is something you&#39;re seeing normally under your traffic patterns, you might want to consider using persistent connections so that you&#39;re not constantly spinning up new sockets.<br />
<br />
<a href='http://www.php.net/manual/en/mysqli.persistconns.php' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://www.php.net/m...ersistconns.php</a>
					
					<br />
					
				</div>
				
				
